RBits

Ye Zheng(dreamhead.cn@gmail.com)

== Overview

RBits is a Ruby library for easy access binary.

== Usage

Basic usage is below and visit TUTORIAL for more advanced usage.

* Create a class to access binary

class Example
  include RBits

  u1 :bit1
  u2 :bit2
  u4 :bit4
end

* Write attributes

e = Example.new
e.bit1 = 1
e.bit2 = 2
e.bit3 = 4

io = StringIO.new
e.write(io) # Now, io.string should be "\001\002\004"

* Read attributes

io = StringIO.new
io.string = "\001\002\004"
e = Example.read(io) # Now, e.bit1 is 1
                     #      e.bit2 is 2
                     #      e.bit4 is 4
